### Iegūst visas sasaistes
GET http://localhost:8080/api/result-assessments
Accept: application/json

###

### Iegūst konkrētu sasaisti pēc ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/result-assessments/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Izveido jaunu sasaisti
POST http://localhost:8080/api/result-assessments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseResult": {
    "id": "COURSE_RESULT_UUID_HERE"
  },
  "component": {
    "id": 1
  },
  "used": true
}

###

### Atjauno esošu sasaisti
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/result-assessments/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseResult": {
    "id": "COURSE_RESULT_UUID_HERE"
  },
  "component": {
    "id": 1
  },
  "used": false
}

###

### Dzēš sasaisti
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/result-assessments/1
